name: FOUND! (Genesis Piece)
description: Re-minting of my first ever NFT, dropped on Hic et Nunc as OBJKT 17894 in 30 March 2021 and burned unsold. Here I present a new version processed from the original raw file with upsampling, advanced noise cancellation and color enhancement. This second version was originally released as HeN OBJKT 126511 on 10 June 2021. Shot 1st February 2011 in the Lapa commercial district of São Paulo in front of a clothing store just before opening. Location: -23.519483, -46.702671.
